{"tid":209840,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性討論]到底動物朋友憑咩咁紅?","createTime":"2017-04-20T13:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T06:48:38.000Z","uid":67667,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"128ad75b263819bd007efe38232be7620c49d648","tid":209840,"uid":67667,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"利伸左先, 我係睇晒嘅,<br />\n但我唔知有咩原因佢而家咁受歡迎,<br />\n佢作畫完全唔入流, 劇情等等都好一般,<br />\n除左設定好似黑少少之外引人討論之外,<br />\n睇完之後都唔知自己睇左乜鳩,<br />\n話佢治癒系倒不如話係幼兒向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點解咁多人吹捧? 我望唔透....<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 首歌係好聽嘅, 有loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b603f9784cfa4fb9215f6720d0ba1c7fb5810c","tid":209840,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"同問胡cfu點解咁紅一樣"},{"pid":"2818d9c2eada26980081358b4e3aef54bf5c5c6a","tid":209840,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"點解my little pony 咁紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7afc01beecce80ef20170b873e362a68a7e8479","tid":209840,"uid":16332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:23:59.000Z","msg":"你係追黎睇定完哂先睇？"},{"pid":"84a35b71cdecba9909c6e340f75bf1c22d27b53f","tid":209840,"uid":46389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"同問"},{"pid":"4b4b58db0dd41a053a3e82d3adb3b4f9262201d9","tid":209840,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:33:23.000Z","msg":"rule 34"},{"pid":"28a640829d9963647dbea56af5bcfdcd8af44b4b","tid":209840,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T15:34:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BnVeX1jxYSg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBnVeX1jxYSg&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm