g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9dc73a10b142a80033df6c28efca5857f4be38d6","tid":209840,"uid":104380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T00:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔啱睇都無辦法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n其他動畫太多添加劑，你見到太多賣肉，賣萌，賣狗血劇情<br />\n<br />\n動物朋友唔會標奇立異，專心做好自已劇本， 就算煮一碗白飯， 你有心煮食落口，都會覺得甜。"},{"pid":"a16b0aadb5a31f98caafbde10b1a375695e40905","tid":209840,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T01:41:24.000Z","msg":"個無里頭級數拍得住動物橫町<br />\n所以會紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b28bdda7c5f4192f21e3c039788bc362dfdb2d","tid":209840,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T02:43:51.000Z","msg":"幾紅都好 過多幾年都會過氣"},{"pid":"c91619778ddb1579bd6a5b0eadd71716860f92f7","tid":209840,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾紅都好 過多幾年都會過氣</blockquote><br />\n第二季應該又爆一次"},{"pid":"62236d971e7b8f8889ca57002958edae2fc58453","tid":209840,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T03:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔啱睇都無辦法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n其他動畫太多添加劑，你見到太多賣肉，賣萌，賣狗血劇情<br />\n<br />\n動物朋友唔會標奇立異，專心做好自已劇本， 就算煮一碗白飯， 你有心煮食落口，都會覺得甜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己就已經睇厭晒d後宮賣肉黑化劇情<br />\n所以呢套真係幾驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82c694641bccfe03bc59b1fab45e87e8b03433ac","tid":209840,"uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"因為一開始零期望, 仲有第一集同人水準<br />\n但繼續睇落去又覺得劇本設定OK, 啲人咪覺得有驚喜<br />\n我自己睇完就唔覺得有幾すーごいー, 有啲直頭on9, 但起碼見到製作係用心整"},{"pid":"e812f13c8b900fe9c0a2c2e36e4f7ed6aac147c1","tid":209840,"uid":38271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T05:01:54.000Z","msg":"主因係而家太多賣廣告動畫連講完一個故事都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伏筆舖排做得幾好<br />\n同埋攞深夜時間播幼兒向(表面)動畫好少有"},{"pid":"68196c1618cdddc567f73990809b4833af65c8bd","tid":209840,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T06:48:38.000Z","msg":"光鮮背後有一段黑暗歷史"}]}